1
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:08,760
Your Highness.

2
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:10,400
Your Highness.

3
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,800
You know you can't hold your liquor,

4
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,920
yet you push yourself at the palace banquet.

5
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,720
Aren't you just making a fool of yourself?

6
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:17,880
I am drunk.

7
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:21,160
Then, could I trouble Miss Yan

8
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:23,020
to help me to the side hall to rest?

9
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:35,479
That was refreshing.

10
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:39,180
There's something wrong with this wine.

11
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,240
Qianji powder, a deadly poison.

12
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,580
The Emperor wants to kill you.

13
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:44,979
We don't know that yet.

14
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,300
Don't move.

15
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,280
There are shadow guards behind you.

16
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,740
Play along with me for now.

17
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,680
Miss Yan.

18
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,400
You rejected the marriage during the day,

19
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,130
proud as a winter plum blossom.

20
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,680
Why, when night falls,

21
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,410
do you come to provoke me again?

22
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:07,120
Are you playing hard to get with me?

23
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:22,720
Lord Xiao,

24
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:24,540
did you find anything?

25
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,200
I did.

26
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:31,360
I, Zhao Zhijing, Vice Minister of Rites,

27
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:33,300
pay my respects to Your Highness.

28
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,560
Dispense with the formalities, Lord Zhao.

29
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,880
I heard the Ministry of Rites recently

30
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,360
stored many rare treasures.

31
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,880
I came specially to take a look.

32
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:41,760
Please feel free to look around, Your Highness.

33
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,440
I will wait outside.

34
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:46,120
If you need anything, just call for me.

35
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,040
The Longlin Dagger.

36
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:22,440
What is the Longlin Dagger?

37
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:24,880
It's a Nanjiang dagger that can cut through gold and stone.

38
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,360
According to the Ministry of Rites' records,

39
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,600
when the late Emperor ascended the throne,

40
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:29,480
Nanjiang presented a pair of Longlin Daggers

41
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:31,280
to him as a congratulatory gift.

42
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:31,920
Later,

43
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,160
the late Emperor bestowed them

44
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:36,320
upon the Empress Dowager and Dowager Consort Xiao,

45
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,720
the current Emperor's biological mother.

46
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:42,480
What does this Longlin Dagger have to do

47
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,920
with my father's disappearance?

48
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:47,000
Since we're already here in the palace,

49
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,560
I'll show Miss Yan around.

50
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:44,060
My father was injured by the Longlin Dagger.

51
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:50,960
Jingyan.

52
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:54,680
Look here.

53
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,280
The date of closing the case

54
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,360
was written with fresh ink,

55
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,090
which shows it was added later.

56
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,200
It seems

57
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,000
the Duke's case is not closed.

58
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,800
This file

59
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,800
is carefully prepared false evidence.

60
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,520
Go.

61
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,120
Come here.

62
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:38,280
The late Emperor deeply favored Dowager Consort Xiao.

63
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:40,210
She soon gave birth to the Emperor.

64
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,720
Seeing her status rise because of her son

65
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,320
and the Emperor's growing favor,

66
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:46,650
the Empress Dowager took vicious action.

67
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,720
She caused Dowager Consort Xiao to miscarry three times,

68
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,780
leaving her permanently infertile.

69
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:51,940
After that,

70
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,920
the late Emperor gradually distanced himself

71
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,380
and no longer favored her.

72
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,800
Dowager Consort Xiao wept through the long nights,

73
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,460
falling ill from depression.

74
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:04,100
She volunteered to be confined in the Cold Palace forever,

75
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,880
spending the rest of her life there.

76
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:08,140
She went to the Cold Palace voluntarily.

77
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,680
As for the Dragon Scale Dagger that stabbed my father,

78
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,400
does it belong to the Empress Dowager

79
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:13,480
or Dowager Consort Xiao?

80
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,940
This Dowager Consort Xiao

81
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,960
has lived deep in the Cold Palace for years.

82
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,480
She had no interactions with the Duke.

83
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,140
Why would there be any grudge?

84
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,960
Gratitude and grudges in this world

85
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,400
are never without roots

86
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:26,920
or a source.

87
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:34,000
Pour all the medicine down her throat!

88
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,280
Pour it all in!

89
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,880
Don't leave a single drop!

90
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:37,680
Hurry up!

91
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,480
Pour it in!

92
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:52,080
Your Highness.

93
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,600
Mother.

94
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,680
Mother.

95
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,159
Mother.

96
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:02,880
Master,

97
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:07,400
Madam died suddenly.

98
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,340
Today at the Hall of Supreme Harmony,

99
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:29,520
why did you...

100
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,200
My grievances are unredressed and vengeance unfulfilled.

101
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:32,530
How can I start a family?

102
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,120
We are already engaged.

103
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,640
I will wait for you.

104
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,840
Although Prince Ling is eliminated,

105
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:41,520
there is only a glimmer of hope to clear my father's name.

106
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,760
We must find the Officials' Records as soon as possible.

107
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,480
Otherwise, the Empress Dowager

108
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,810
won't let us off easily.

109
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,200
In that case,

110
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,680
let's strike first

111
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,760
and play the victim.

112
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,400
Eat it.

113
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,880
Top-grade jade dust from Myanmar

114
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:07,160
is incomparable to your usual coarse grain.

115
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,600
Your Majesty,

116
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:13,640
I have been very anxious lately.

117
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,600
Ever since the Emperor obtained the Imperial Seal,

118
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,920
he rarely comes to Zichen Palace to pay his respects.

119
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,720
Today,

120
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:23,240
he deployed the Jinlin Guards and the Imperial Army for a drill again.

121
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,760
I am worried.

122
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,880
It's fine.

123
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,240
Having been a puppet for so long

124
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,880
and newly ascending to the throne,

125
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:33,480
it's inevitable he would indulge in the taste of absolute power.

126
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:35,840
The secret edict left by the late Emperor to the Emperor

127
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:38,000
to restrain me has been burned.

128
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,039
I fear nothing.

129
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,799
Having fought with that Lady Xiao for half my life,

130
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:45,460
I finally beat her by one move.

131
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,720
Now,

132
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,530
I am the esteemed Empress Dowager.

133
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,520
The Emperor calls me Mother.

134
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:55,400
Would he dare commit matricide without cause?

135
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:58,450
But the Emperor is ultimately born of that Lady Xiao.

136
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:01,960
The past grievances between you and Lady Xiao are not settled.

137
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,120
I'm afraid that

138
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:07,560
if he is out to condemn you, he can always trump up a charge.

139
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,840
Empress Dowager.

140
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,800
The Emperor and Dowager Consort Xiao are heading to Zichen Palace.

141
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,320
They are accompanied by the heir of Marquis Zhenbei

142
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,960
and the daughter of Duke Yan.

143
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,760
Nanny Zhang,

144
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,720
fetch my wedding dress.

145
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,440
Filing a false countercharge

146
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,680
is a risky move.

147
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:48,280
If we fail, neither of us will have a way out.

148
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,960
What? Are you scared?

149
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,120
I'm afraid of hurting the innocent.

150
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:52,960
You and I

151
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,560
share life and death,

152
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:57,090
along with honor and disgrace.

153
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,120
Even though I live deep in the Cold Palace,

154
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,450
the Empress Dowager still won't let me go.

155
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,880
Heir of Marquis Zhenbei,

156
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:24,040
you trespassed into Zichen Palace twice.

157
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:26,440
Do you really think nothing of the state laws?

158
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,440
Empress Dowager,

159
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,600
do you still remember this person?

160
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,520
Absurd.

161
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:36,760
How could I know such an insignificant person?

162
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:40,440
This man is a Black Armor Guard from Prince Ling's estate,

163
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:43,200
but actually a trusted follower of the Empress Dowager.

164
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,960
He confessed everything before he died.

165
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,890
Three years ago,

166
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,930
Prince Ling held a private banquet

167
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:50,080
to kill the Duke,

168
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:54,170
using the Dragon Scale Dagger bestowed by the Empress Dowager.

169
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:59,000
And Prince Ling colluded with the Northern Di,

170
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,960
smuggling arms

171
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,280
without any hindrance.

172
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,080
It was based on

173
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:06,880
the official document stamped with the Empress Dowager's phoenix seal.

174
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,240
Here is the Dragon Scale Dagger.

175
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,370
And here is the file of the Duke's case.

176
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,600
Empress Dowager,

177
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:14,700
do you have anything else to say in your defense?

178
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,160
You are...

179
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,400
There is no proof since he is dead.

180
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,400
This is a frame-up.

181
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:20,400
You talk too much.

182
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:21,920
Beat him to death.

183
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,560
This.

184
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,960
Empress Dowager.

185
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,240
Empress Dowager.

186
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:35,090
The Longlin Dagger was bestowed by the late emperor.

187
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,360
How could I give it away?

188
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,560
Lady Xiao,

189
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:41,640
don't you have one too?

190
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:45,320
Mother, you summoned me urgently.

191
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,380
What is the matter?

192
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:48,970
This Longlin Dagger

193
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,440
was personally bestowed by the late emperor.

194
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,640
I have always kept it hidden in the bedside drawer.

195
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:54,970
I never dared to move it.

196
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,200
Today, while cleaning, I discovered

197
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:57,960
that this one

198
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,760
is not mine at all.

199
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:01,490
It belongs to Lady Wang.

200
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,260
Mother, how can you be sure

201
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:06,280
that this dagger belongs to Lady Wang?

202
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,240
I remember

203
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,160
the two Dragon Scale Daggers are identical in shape.

204
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,840
There should be no difference.

205
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,770
My dagger had a crescent mark here,

206
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:15,960
personally carved by the late emperor.

207
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:20,560
Empress Dowager.

208
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:22,080
You already hold ultimate power.

209
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,010
Why do you still refuse to let me go?

210
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:26,520
You chant sutras and worship Buddha all day long.

211
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:28,520
Why is your obsession still so deep?

212
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:33,040
Ultimate power?

213
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:38,920
So what if I hold ultimate power?

214
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:42,120
In the end, I still couldn't get the love I wanted.

215
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:46,840
And I was forced into this situation by my rebellious son and treacherous officials.

216
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,840
Empress Dowager.

217
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,440
Why did you collude with Prince Ling

218
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:52,960
and allow him to commit treason?

219
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:54,730
And why did you order him

220
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:57,840
to brutally attack the Duke?

221
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:02,440
I allowed him to commit treason?

222
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:13,480
What a great play of using another's knife to kill.

223
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:14,880
Exactly.

224
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:18,080
I just wanted to use the Xiao family's knife

225
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:20,320
to kill the late Emperor's loyal officials.

226
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:23,080
If it fails, the Xiao family will pay with their lives.

227
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,010
With the Emperor under my control,

228
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:28,240
I can hold the imperial seal forever

229
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:30,000
and firmly manipulate the puppet.

230
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,680
Wang!

231
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:33,800
You are insane!

232
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,000
This title 'Wang'

233
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:40,720
sounds much more genuine than that hypocritical

234
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:42,400
'Mother'.

235
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:46,240
Emperor.

236
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:50,080
Look at the wolves and scorpions in this court.

237
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:53,160
Which of them isn't a flesh-eating monster?

238
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:54,940
This dragon throne...

239
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,440
Can you really sit on it securely?

240
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,080
Empress Dowager.

241
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,360
Where is my father?

242
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,280
Is he dead or alive?

243
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:05,840
The Duke.

244
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:10,360
He was stabbed by Cui Tingru

245
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:12,280
with the Xiao family's Dragon Scale Dagger.

246
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:14,010
He was stabbed multiple times,

247
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,740
each missing the vital parts.

248
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:17,800
He cannot live,

249
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,840
and he cannot die.

250
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,660
Don't believe her.

251
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,000
She is provoking you.

252
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,620
Empress Dowager Wang,

253
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,580
for colluding with rebels

254
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:30,360
and murdering loyal officials,

255
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:32,440
is hereby stripped of her titles.

256
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:36,250
She shall be confined to the Cold Palace forever.

257
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,080
Empress Dowager.

258
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:48,960
Xiao,

259
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:55,120
this Nine Phoenix Crown should be buried in the mausoleum.

260
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,440
And you,

261
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,100
are not worthy.

262
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,840
Empress Dowager,

263
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:04,720
tell me exactly where my father is.

264
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:07,560
Is he alive or dead?

265
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:08,360
Tell me.

266
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:09,040
Qingshu.

267
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,240
Tell me.

268
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:16,600
The emperor poisoned my parrot.

269
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:19,060
If the emperor breaks the law,

270
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:21,800
he commits the same crime as the commoners.

271
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,240
Same crime.

272
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,400
Same crime.

273
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:33,360
Wang,

274
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,760
let this thirty years of resentment

275
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,400
end here.

276
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,240
Cuimei.

277
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:16,320
Mei.

278
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:16,840
Cuimei.

279
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:19,120
Yong.

280
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:20,640
Weikun Huachao.

281
